Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說等一下再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海太容易發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香你不也在慪氣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是一千日元的漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩躁的時候果然得大吃一頓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也填飽了  去優香家看錄像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再稍微練習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我家一年裏最可怕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸山先生  出租車已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  歡迎光臨  請到這裏辦理手續
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和誰發短信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（挺棘手的）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}（放棄的話就完了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香有在反省嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  她可是優香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「夏海已經不生氣了嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我已經不生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能  她可是夏海啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是容易發火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天絕對是優香不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做女人真虧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候心想長大後一定要扛著道具去參加太鼓祭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可是很吃力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人抬著都搖搖晃晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每年都會有人身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請起身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個喝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是很想試試嘛  難得的祭典果然還是要好好活躍一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不扛道具  夏海的媽媽表現也很突出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今年我們不是也要參加歌手大會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是大活躍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想加油不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年已經是最後一次我們四個人可以一起努力的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  優香  剛才你說過吧  春的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(391,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把那個練習完美的話  紗季和夏海肯定會大吃一驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜你真是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去凜家裏看錄像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後也要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  還要換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衣服忘記帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香那傢伙開溜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子專挑忙的日子逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋  我絕對不會饒了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都戴上的話不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 你來幫忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來確實每年都這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 她沒跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季 你穿好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正要穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有點渾身不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉緊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的腰圍很細 不別起來的話就不好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是收得太緊的話總感覺不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跑起來也不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了這衣服就不要去想跑步什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然紗季幫我弄了之後感覺就完全不一樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是為什麼呢 太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒也要幫那兩個人弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我也該換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香她們有在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看凜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香一定不會練的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙絕對不會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海 我在放暑假前  完全沒想過自己會參加歌手大會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在卻變得如此認真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信這會成為我重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海我問你  這都是多虧了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她竟然說要作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得玩水氣球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前玩水氣球的時候 優香不是每次都會第一個逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  優香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢 會濕透的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人玩水氣球還怕會濕透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是優香最後還拿個超大的水氣球來反擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都會半途掉下來自取滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好工口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,333)\fs18}好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是中學生該有的性感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海和紗季一定不會逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不逃就會渾身濕透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們要是逃了  我就會成為大家的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我跑得慢  所以夏海和紗季要是逃了大家就會全都瞄準我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此她們才會不逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是夏的舞步讓人感覺更加輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(233,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來優香也一起來跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想看春的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(339,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場演唱會春的舞步是跳得最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(282,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我優香也是把一切都賭在了這次歌手大會上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧  凜  我可要動真格了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上還是晴天的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雨下得還真大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨的話會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手大會的宣傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天中止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是練習的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明祭典並不中止的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雨停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  我們讓雨停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算作弊  我覺得這不算作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算讓雨停下來  也不會左右歌手大會的勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就兩個願望一起許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望雨停下來  然後我們獲得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須四個人一起努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和優香  夏海  紗季一起努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才會成為最寶貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:17:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要參加今天的歌手大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但是這種天氣的話可能會中止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那要快點把雨停下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雨停下來的許願方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎  向神石許願讓雨停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  要去許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  這才像夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「像」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是優香她們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們許願了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許了希望雨停下來的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們兩個人改變了天氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年就要變得冷清了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我女兒也是剛搬到這裏就交到了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的獲得優勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方獲得優勝是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  我們要從這裏開始起步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}成為真正的偶像團體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}順利通過試鏡  讓我們進去東京的藝能界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}然後出席各大活動來積攢人氣  我們的目標可是武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  真的是你們兩個人把天氣改變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向神石許願了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽教我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴天娃娃？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和優香一起向晴天娃娃許願之後  天就一下子放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（佐奈要是也來看了就好了）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是神的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是的  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就真的要出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去試鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜我們在歌手大會上獲得了優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先想要把這個消息告訴誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感謝憧憬著能在普通組獲得優勝的過去的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:23:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去要去  去什麼地方玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇跡  第八話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂鬱的four trips
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,four trips是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.33,0:24:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像啦 想像
